snippet.title: Real Reason Amber Heard Could End Up Behind Bars
snippet.description:
In this video we are going to talk about the real reason why amber heard could end up behind the bars. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
___________________________________________

Amber Heard filed for divorce on May 23, 2016, just 15 months after their marriage in the Bahamas. Though Heard filed a document of more than 300 pages including photos of herself covered in scratches and bruises when she initially accused Johnny Depp of abuse, new details suggest she may have faked some of that "evidence."
